you're trying to check out branches/RELEASE_3_4/madman/Rpacks/GenVisR 
into the same directory.

Don't do that, check out the release branch into a different directory, 
e.g,.

   mkdir -p RELEASE_3_4/madman/Rpacks
   cd RELEASE_3_4/madman/Rpacks
   svn co 
